---
title: Video Player QoE State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2

    %% ── States ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    %%
    %%  Idle         No video source loaded; initial state after init or reset.
    %%  Loading      Source assigned; fetching manifest / metadata.
    %%  Ready        Metadata loaded; player paused at start position.
    %%  PlayAttempt  play() called; awaiting first decoded frame.
    %%               ⏱ VIDEO START TIME begins here.
    %%               ⏱ WATCHED TIME begins here.
    %%  Buffering    play() called but buffer is empty; downloading initial segment.
    %%               ⏱ VIDEO START TIME continues accumulating.
    %%  Playing      Frames actively being decoded and rendered.
    %%               ⏱ PLAYED TIME accumulates.
    %%  Paused       Playback suspended by user or system; position held.
    %%  Seeking      Seek requested; position changing, frames not rendered.
    %%  Rebuffering  Was Playing; buffer exhausted mid-playback; stalled.
    %%               ⏱ REBUFFER TIME accumulates.
    %%  Ended        Playback reached end of content naturally.
    %%  Error        Fatal, unrecoverable player error.
    %%
    %%  WATCHED TIME spans all states from PlayAttempt until Ended or destroy().
    %%
    %% ── Beacon Emissions ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    %%
    %%  Transition                                  Beacon(s) emitted
    %%  ──────────────────────────────────────────  ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    %%  Ready → PlayAttempt [play()]                play  (seq=0; no state/metrics; carries video/client/sdk)
    %%  Ended → PlayAttempt [play() replay]         play  (seq=0; new session, new play_id)
    %%  PlayAttempt|Buffering → Playing [firstFrame] first_frame  +  playing  (same timestamp; VST now known)
    %%  Playing → Paused [pause()]                  pause
    %%  Playing → Seeking [seek]                    seek
    %%  Playing → Rebuffering [stall]               stall
    %%  Playing → Ended [ended event]               completed
    %%  Playing → Error                             error
    %%  Paused → PlayAttempt [play()]               playing  (resume; same session)
    %%  Seeking → Playing [playing event]           playing  (seek resolved by JS debounce)
    %%  Seeking → Rebuffering [seekEnd buffer empty] stall
    %%  Seeking → Paused [seekEnd prev==Paused]     (no beacon; stays paused)
    %%  Rebuffering → Playing [playing event]       playing  (stall recovery)
    %%  Rebuffering → Paused [pause()]              playing  +  pause
    %%  Rebuffering → Seeking [seek]                playing  +  seek
    %%  Any active state [destroy()]                ended
    %%  Any active state [heartbeat tick]           heartbeat  (when silent for heartbeat_interval_ms)
    %%
    %%  "Active" states: PlayAttempt, Buffering, Playing, Paused, Seeking, Rebuffering.

    [*] --> Idle : init

    %% ── Loading ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Idle      --> Loading     : load(src)
    Loading   --> Ready       : canPlay / metadata loaded
    Loading   --> Error       : error event

    %% ── Play Initiation ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Ready     --> PlayAttempt : play()
    Ready     --> Idle        : destroy()

    PlayAttempt --> Buffering : waiting (buffer empty)
    PlayAttempt --> Playing   : firstFrame / playing
    PlayAttempt --> Error     : error event

    Buffering   --> Playing   : firstFrame / playing
    Buffering   --> Error     : error event

    %% ── Active Playback ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Playing --> Paused        : pause()
    Playing --> Seeking       : seek
    Playing --> Rebuffering   : stall (buffer stall)
    Playing --> Ended         : ended event
    Playing --> Error         : error event

    %% ── Paused ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Paused  --> PlayAttempt   : play()
    Paused  --> Seeking       : seek
    Paused  --> Idle          : destroy()

    %% ── Seeking ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    %% JS integrations resolve seeks by sending a playing event after a 300ms debounce.
    Seeking --> Playing       : playing event (debounce resolved, video playing)
    Seeking --> Error         : error event

    %% ── Rebuffering ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Rebuffering --> Playing   : playing event
    Rebuffering --> Paused    : pause()
    Rebuffering --> Seeking   : seek
    Rebuffering --> Error     : error event

    %% ── Terminal / Reset ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Ended --> PlayAttempt     : play() [replay]
    Ended --> Loading         : load(newSrc)
    Ended --> Idle            : destroy() / reset()

    Error --> Loading         : load(src) [retry]
    Error --> Idle            : destroy() / reset()
    Error --> [*]             : unrecoverable / GC
